channel.title: What happened to Auxcast?
channel.description: Auxcast is a Soundcloud Channel that promotes Auxy users and tell everybody more about them. It was abandoned a few months ago and I’m wondering what has happened to it. Anybody know why it was abandoned?

item.title: What happened to Auxcast?
item.dc:creator: Polar
item.description:
It was about to come back multiple times, but constantly abandoned again before the first episode. A bunch of different people have picked it up as hosts but ended up not having time. Maybe someday someone will come along and do the trick.
